graph LR
    DSPO[Data Science Pipelines Operator]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    DSPO -->|container platform| OpenShift[OpenShift/Kubernetes 4.11+]
    DSPO -->|v2 workflow engine| Argo[Argo Workflows<br/>Latest stable]
