    %% Integration Points
    KFP_SDK[KFP SDK v2] -->|pipeline submission| DSPO
    Elyra[Elyra] -->|visual authoring| DSPO
    Prometheus[Prometheus] -->|monitoring| DSPO

    %% Component relationships
    DSPO -->|creates CRs| Argo
    DSPO -->|creates CRs| Tekton

